  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you've learned how to produce exactly the tool you need: with @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-items.HWphIyqLmXJ56fRh]{Thieves' Tools} or @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-journals.ak9Gz7zi41IOXlIQ]{Artisan's Tools} in hand, you can magically create one set of artisan's tools in an unoccupied space within 5 feet of you. This creation requires 1 hour of uninterrupted work, which can coincide with a <strong>short </strong>or <strong>long rest</strong>. Though the product of magic, the tools are nonmagical, and they vanish when you use this feature again.</p>",
